It is difficult to determine without further information, but the highest recorded temperature in Madeira during November was 28°C (82°F) on November 9th, 2017. The lowest recorded temperature in Madeira during November was 8.2°C (46°F) on November 29th, 2003.

The average maximum temperature for Madeira in November is about 22°C (71°F), while the average minimum temperature is around15°C(59° F). It's important to note that weather can vary from year to year and these numbers are only historical averages that give you an idea of what to expect during your visit.
